{"id":"the-singing-frog","slug":"the-singing-frog","title":"The Singing Frog","title_ko":"노래하는 개구리","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/cover.webp","summary_ko":"밤마다 혼자 노래하던 개구리가 용기를 내어 연못 친구들과 함께 합창을 이끄는 이야기예요.","wordCount":120,"pages":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"A green frog sat on a lily pad.","translation_ko":"초록 개구리가 연잎 위에 앉아 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"green","charStart":2,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":680},{"word":"frog","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":1060},{"word":"sat","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1460},{"word":"on","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1660},{"word":"a","charStart":20,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1800},{"word":"lily","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1800,"endMs":1980},{"word":"pad","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2260}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Every night, he sang a quiet song.","translation_ko":"밤마다 개구리는 조용한 노래를 불렀어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"night","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":300,"endMs":600},{"word":"he","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":780,"endMs":1020},{"word":"sang","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1160},{"word":"a","charStart":21,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1500},{"word":"quiet","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1720},{"word":"song","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2060}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"He sang only in the dark.","translation_ko":"개구리는 어두울 때만 노래했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"sang","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":360,"endMs":640},{"word":"only","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":640,"endMs":1060},{"word":"in","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1280},{"word":"the","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1460},{"word":"dark","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1700}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"He was shy, so he sang alone.","translation_ko":"수줍음이 많아서 혼자서만 노래를 불렀거든요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":160},{"word":"was","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":160,"endMs":360},{"word":"shy","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":360,"endMs":680},{"word":"so","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1280},{"word":"he","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1560},{"word":"sang","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1660},{"word":"alone","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2000}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"One night, a fish heard the song.","translation_ko":"어느 날 밤, 물고기 한 마리가 그 노래를 들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"night","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":320,"endMs":660},{"word":"a","charStart":11,"charEnd":12,"startMs":740,"endMs":1340},{"word":"fish","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1400},{"word":"heard","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1760},{"word":"the","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2000},{"word":"song","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2300}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"That is so pretty!\" she said.","translation_ko":"\"정말 예쁜 노래야!\" 물고기가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"That","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":1000},{"word":"is","charStart":6,"charEnd":8,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1240},{"word":"so","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1740},{"word":"pretty","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2640},{"word":"she","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2820},{"word":"said","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3060}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"The frog stopped and hid his face.","translation_ko":"개구리는 노래를 멈추고 얼굴을 가렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"frog","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":520},{"word":"stopped","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":520,"endMs":960},{"word":"and","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":960,"endMs":1480},{"word":"hid","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1660},{"word":"his","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1900},{"word":"face","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2220}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Please sing again,\" said the fish.","translation_ko":"\"다시 불러 줘.\" 물고기가 부탁했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Please","charStart":1,"charEnd":7,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"sing","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":440,"endMs":700},{"word":"again","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":700,"endMs":1260},{"word":"said","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1600},{"word":"the","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1780},{"word":"fish","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2060}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"So the frog took a deep breath.","translation_ko":"그래서 개구리는 깊게 숨을 들이쉬었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"the","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":380,"endMs":580},{"word":"frog","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":580,"endMs":880},{"word":"took","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":880,"endMs":1160},{"word":"a","charStart":17,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1460},{"word":"deep","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1660},{"word":"breath","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2000}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"Then he sang, and the fish smiled.","translation_ko":"그러고는 노래를 불렀고, 물고기는 미소 지었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"he","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":360,"endMs":680},{"word":"sang","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":1040},{"word":"and","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1580},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1740},{"word":"fish","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2000},{"word":"smiled","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2480}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"A bird and a turtle came to listen.","translation_ko":"새와 거북이도 노래를 들으러 다가왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"bird","charStart":2,"charEnd":6,"startMs":240,"endMs":520},{"word":"and","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":520,"endMs":780},{"word":"a","charStart":11,"charEnd":12,"startMs":780,"endMs":1200},{"word":"turtle","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1220},{"word":"came","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1700},{"word":"to","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2000},{"word":"listen","charStart":28,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2160}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Can we sing with you?\" they asked.","translation_ko":"\"우리도 같이 불러도 돼?\" 둘이 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Can","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"we","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":300,"endMs":560},{"word":"sing","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":560,"endMs":760},{"word":"with","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":760,"endMs":980},{"word":"you","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":980,"endMs":1800},{"word":"they","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1800,"endMs":1940},{"word":"asked","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2320}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"The frog felt warm and happy.","translation_ko":"개구리는 마음이 따뜻하고 행복해졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"frog","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":600},{"word":"felt","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":600,"endMs":1080},{"word":"warm","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1460},{"word":"and","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1800},{"word":"happy","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2040}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Yes! Let's sing together,\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"좋아! 우리 함께 부르자.\" 개구리가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Yes","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":1080},{"word":"Let's","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1560,"endMs":2000},{"word":"sing","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2200},{"word":"together","charStart":17,"charEnd":25,"startMs":2200,"endMs":3020},{"word":"he","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3180},{"word":"said","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":3180,"endMs":3400}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"The frog led the song.","translation_ko":"개구리가 노래를 이끌었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":840},{"word":"frog","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":840,"endMs":1140},{"word":"led","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1400},{"word":"the","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1620},{"word":"song","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1880}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"The whole pond began to sing.","translation_ko":"연못 전체가 노래하기 시작했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"whole","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":220,"endMs":660},{"word":"pond","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":660,"endMs":1080},{"word":"began","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1540},{"word":"to","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1900},{"word":"sing","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2140}]}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-singing-frog-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"Now the frog is not shy.","translation_ko":"이제 개구리는 부끄러워하지 않아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"the","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":360,"endMs":600},{"word":"frog","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":600,"endMs":880},{"word":"is","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":880,"endMs":1180},{"word":"not","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1460},{"word":"shy","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1720}]},{"id":"the-singing-frog-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"Every night, all the pond friends sing together.","translation_ko":"밤마다 연못 친구들이 모두 함께 노래해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-singing-frog/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"night","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":340,"endMs":600},{"word":"all","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":820,"endMs":1080},{"word":"the","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1460},{"word":"pond","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1560},{"word":"friends","charStart":26,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1920},{"word":"sing","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2160},{"word":"together","charStart":39,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2500}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"개구리는 어디에 앉아 있었나요?","type":"mc","options":["연잎 위","바위 위","나무 위","모래 위"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"개구리는 작은 초록 연잎 위에 앉아 노래했어요.","id":"the-singing-frog-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"개구리는 처음에 언제 노래했나요?","type":"mc","options":["아침에","낮에","밤에","비 올 때"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"개구리는 연못이 어두워지는 밤마다 노래했어요.","id":"the-singing-frog-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"개구리의 노래를 가장 먼저 들은 동물은 누구인가요?","type":"mc","options":["새","거북이","물고기","오리"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"물고기가 가장 먼저 노래를 듣고 예쁘다고 칭찬했어요.","id":"the-singing-frog-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"새와 거북이는 개구리에게 무엇을 물었나요?","type":"mc","options":["같이 불러도 되는지","노래를 멈춰 달라고","집이 어디인지","물이 어디인지"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"새와 거북이는 함께 노래해도 되는지 물었어요.","id":"the-singing-frog-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 우리에게 알려 주는 것은 무엇일까요?","type":"mc","options":["혼자 있는 게 가장 좋다","용기를 내면 함께 즐거워진다","노래는 어렵다","밤은 무섭다"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"부끄러움을 이기고 용기를 내자 모두가 함께 노래하는 기쁨을 나누게 되었어요.","id":"the-singing-frog-q5","ord":4}]}